cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper deals with detecting and resolving bias in decision-support queries, which is a problem related to data management and analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Database), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves statistical analysis and fairness, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
